GOTO_TIP: Teleports you to the selected player.
BRING_TIP: Brings the selected player to you.
SEND_TO_TIP: Sends the selected player to another player.
SEND_TO_LOCATION_TIP: Sends the selected player to a location on the map.
DARWIN_MODE_TIP:
Toggles invulnerability and infinite
ammo on the selected player(s).
ERROR_CANT_GOTO: Failed to find a valid location near the specified player.
ERROR_CANT_GOTO_LOCATION: Failed to find a valid position at the specified location.
ERROR_CANT_BRING: Failed to find a valid location near you.
ERROR_CANT_SEND_TO_SELF: You cannot send a player to themselves.
ERROR_CANT_SET_DARWIN_MODE: Failed to set darwin mode on the specified player(s).
